        public static SubroAdversePartyBuilder uiReadySubroAdverseParty()
        Creates a new, ui ready, SubroAdversePartyBuilder with the following fields set
        • SubrogationSummary - set to a UI ready subrogation summary that uses an existing claim or creates new auto claim
        • SubroGovernmentInvolved - a randomly selected government involved type
        • Fault - a unique positive number
        • Classification - a randomly selected classification type
        • Strategy - a randomly selected strategy type
        • ExpectedRecovery - a unique positive number

          a new ui ready builder
